description: Corey Feldman was a child actor in the 1980s, who appeared in such films as The Goonies, Stand By Me, and The Lost Boys. More recently, he has embarked upon a career as a musician and as a voice actor in Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles and Cartoon Network's Robot Chicken. He often appeared in films with the late Corey Haim, and was deeply affected by Haim's death. Feldman has struggled with substance abuse.
name: Corey Feldman
